room_title: Escape room "Sorcerer's Quest" by Axxiom Escape Rooms in Newark
room_address: 280 E Main Street Unit 132, Newark, DE 19711
room_description: Magic and mystery await all who dare enter the Dragon's Lair. The Dark Lord has returned and it's up to you as wizards to vanquish him forever. The headmaster's chamber contains secrets that must be revealed if you have any chance of defeating the Dark Lord once and for all. Gather your army and finish what you started.
